PJ_BEGIN_DECL pj_status_t pjmedia_snd_aps_set_route ( pjmedia_snd_stream *  stream,
pjmedia_snd_route  route 
)

Set audio routing for APS sound device.

Parameters:
stream The sound device stream, the stream should be started before calling this function.
route Audio routing to be set.
Returns:
PJ_SUCCESS on success.
